p.cl:
With these witnesses: William bishop of Moray, legate of the Apostolic See;
                  Gregory, bishop of Dunkeld; Andrew of Caithness, Samson of
                  Brechin, bishops; Geoffrey, abbot of Dunfermline; William,
                  abbot of Melrose; Alured, abbot of Stirling; Isaac, prior of
                  Scone; Walter, prior of Kelso; Matthew the archdeacon;
                  Thorald, archdeacon of Lothian; Master Andrew; Master
                  Herbert; Robert son of Sæwulf, the bishop’s chancellor; Roger
                  the chaplain of Perth; Nicholas the king’s chancellor;
                  Richard the king’s chaplain; Serlo the clerk; David Oliphant;
                  Ferteth, earl of Strathearn; Malcolm, earl of Atholl; Gille
                  Brigte, earl of Angus; Duncan, earl of Fife; Merleswain; Ness
                  son of William; Stephen the clerk.
